Product description

The Wenger 17.5" ScanSmart Laptop Backpack marries contemporary design with innovative storage solutions. Crafted from durable polyester, this backpack means business. This classic backpack is simple yet stylish. Its minimalistic look makes it the ideal accessory to take along to the office, college, school or on trips. Brought to you by Wenger, a renowned Swiss company since 1893.

From the manufacturer

Wenger retained its distinct identity after the takeover by Victorinox Group in 2005. The precision, functionality, thoughtfulness & attention to detail is what underlines the Wenger collection of watches and travel gear which draws on a winning combination of Swiss engineering & reliability. Created in modern designs & using high-grade material, Wenger products are for those who want to count on a Swiss brand at a reasonable cost.

We invariably focus on quality, always innovating and adding much joy to ensure that our designs will become your best buddy while travelling. So, if you are looking for a lightweight yet durable suitcase, a backpack or a travel accessory with several cool features and extra packing space, we promise you’ll find one that ticks all of your boxes within our range! So, let's start packing, shall we?

Whether packing for everyday routine, vacation time, college or office, or a getaway trip with your friends, our backpacks ensure you're well-equipped and on-trend. We have a quality backpack for the style-savvy traveller in you. When you’re ready to move up to a different league of organization in a backpack, this is the one you want.

What sets us apart?

A bag that reflects your life!

Now breeze through airport security with ease as it offers superior protection for your laptop at airport security controls and a dedicated tablet pocket. Travel with confidence with your valuable items securely stored in your well-built backpack.

Laptop & Tablet Pocket

Padded laptop compartment with an essentials organizer that keeps power cords, chargers & business cards neat & accessible. Keep your laptop & tablet secure in its own convenient pocket.

Stay Organized

An ample main compartment integrates a mesh adapters zip pocket for cords, chargers and other tech accessories. While weaving through airport traffic, grab a cool drink from its side zip pockets.

Optimum Comfort

Padded grab handle provides maximum comfort when carrying the backpack by hand. Quickly tighten or loosen the shoulder straps to your desired fit with these convenient thumb-ring adjusters. & Airflow back padding keeps the wearer cool.

Dimesions: 46 x 24 x 35 cm

Weight: 0.9 kg
